label day9_goro_be:
    hide yoshi2_biker
    hide yoshi2 sad4
    show yoshi_biker at left2
    show yoshi worry2 at left2
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24_line1
    yo "What was the reason then…?"

    $ renpy.music.stop(channel='music', fadeout = 1.0)
    scene cgg11 1 with fade
    play music buddy_oath_goro_sad loop
    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line1
    g "I… I’m already content…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line2
    g "To me, Camp Buddy is already perfect the way it is…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line3
    g "To start, we’ve received so many amazing chances already and regained what we nearly lost the previous term…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line4
    g "Now we’ve made it even bigger in such a short period of time… and to receive yet another opportunity was just so unexpected... "

    show cgg11 2 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line5
    g "And honestly…. It’s something I don’t aspire for anymore…"

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24_line2
    yo "Wh-What do you mean…?"

    show cgg11 3 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line6
    g "Don’t get me wrong… I love Camp Buddy with all my heart. It’s my lifelong dream that I had the honor of sharing with everyone, especially you…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line7
    g "But… I’ve been holding on to this place for so long, believing it’s the only thing that makes all of us happy…"

    show cgg11 4 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24_line3
    yo "B-But… I don’t understand… This is what we’ve all been working for."

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24_line4
    yo "It’s just all too sudden… after everything we’ve been through…"

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24_line5
    yo "What changed…?"

    $ renpy.music.stop(channel='music', fadeout = 1.0)
    show cgg11 5 with Dissolve(0.25)
    $ renpy.pause (1.0, hard=True)
    g "..."

    show cgg11 6 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line9
    g "I’m afraid."

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24_line6
    yo "O-Of what…?"

    show cgg11 7 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line10
    g "I’m afraid of the past repeating itself…"

    play music buddy_oath_goro_tragic loop
    yo "...!"

    show cgg11 8 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line11
    g "When I was dealing with all the problems with my ex-wife, I didn’t feel the full extent of the pain because you were there to distract me…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line12
    g "Then you left to pursue your dream to become a scoutmaster, and the effects of my divorce finally hit me."
    yo "..."

    show cgg11 10 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line1
    g "The only thing I had left was to try and make Camp Buddy the best it could be…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line18
    g "I put all my blood, sweat, and tears into it… expanding over and over with blind ambition, until it grew into something I could barely handle…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line19
    g "What I didn’t realize was that I was doing it to cover the pain inside…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line21
    g "I tried numbing myself from any emotion, convinced that I had to stay strong and tough, always…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line23
    g "I let no one see my weakness, and it started a vicious cycle where I grew more and more bitter each day…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24_line24
    g "The dream we had lost all its spirit, turning the camp into a soulless business, and I completely lost touch of what it was supposed to be…"

    show cgg11 11 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24_line7
    yo "I… didn’t know you had to go through all that, Goro…"

    show cgg11 9 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line2
    g "But still… 	I should’ve respected your right to make your own choice…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line3
    g "I was taking away an opportunity not only from the camp, but from you… all for my own selfish reasons…   "

    show cgg11 11 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line1
    yo "But I understand, Goro… "

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line2
    yo "You don’t deserve to suffer like that again, just because we aren’t satisfied with what we have…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line4
    g "I’ve been sacrificing myself for the camp and everyone else this whole time, but never really pursued my own happiness… "

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line5
    g "This new opportunity only made me realize that I’m going to commit myself to something beyond my limits again…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line6
    g "I just want to move on to a new chapter… And I want you in it…"

    show cgg11 2 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line3
    yo "Wh-What are you trying to say…?"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line7
    g "After we finish this project… Let’s leave the camp."

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line4
    yo "Wh-What?!"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line8
    g "We’ve both done so much for a such long time. This is our chance to be happy together…!"

    show cgg11 4 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line5
    yo "I-I don’t understand…! There’s no reason why we can’t be together and still stay at the camp!"

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line6
    yo "Y-You don’t even have to bear the burden anymore…! You can leave everything up to me!"

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line7
    yo "After everything you taught me, I’m ready to lead and make the decisions, so they won’t burden you anymore!"

    show cgg11 5 with Dissolve(0.25)
    g "..."

    show cgg11 4 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line8
    yo "We can’t just leave the camp… What’ll happen to everyone else?"

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line9
    yo "This wasn’t just our dream together, it’s theirs’ too…"

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line10
    yo "I know you’re tired, but there must be another way…!"

    show cgg11 9 with Dissolve(0.25)
    g "..."

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line9
    g "You’re right…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line10
    g "I shouldn’t make everyone else pay the price just for my own desires… "

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line11
    g "It was unfair and narrow-minded of me to even think like that…"

    show cgg11 11 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line11
    yo "You don’t have to give up on your own happiness and continue with the camp either…"

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line12
    yo "We’re all here to help… I’m here to help…"

    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line12
    g "Yoshinori…"

    show cgg11 4 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line13
    yo "You can rely on me from now on! Just believe in me!"
    g "..."

    show cgg11 13 with Dissolve(0.25)
    voice audio.goro_vsg24b_line13
    g "I will fulfill my duties until the end of our commitment… and count on you wholeheartedly for the future, Yoshinori…  "

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line14
    yo "I’m glad you trust me, Goro… I’m really grateful for everything you’ve done for me and the camp this whole time."

    voice audio.yoshi_vsg24b_line15
    yo "I promise, you won’t regret it!"

    scene cg black with fade
    yo "{i}After our talk, Goro drove us both home in silence…{/i}"
    yo "{i}I can’t believe that I never saw how he was losing heart for the camp… There must be something else that I missed…{/i}"

    $ renpy.music.stop(channel='music', fadeout = 1.0)
    $ renpy.music.stop(channel='bgsound', fadeout = 1.0)
    $ renpy.music.stop(channel='bgsound2', fadeout = 1.0)
    scene cg black
    hide screen location
    hide screen timeline
    hide screen quick_menu
    $quick_menu = False
    with fade
    play sound sleeping_time
    $ time_transition_night_to_day_winter2()
    $ renpy.pause (2.0, hard=True)
    jump day10_goro_be
